## Registration Flow

### Email + Password
Form collects: **Full Name ¬∑ Email ¬∑ Phone ¬∑ Batch ¬∑ Session From ¬∑ Session To ¬∑ Roll Number ¬∑ Password**

Key UX: live **class name preview** appears once all three (Batch + Session From + Session To) are valid:
> `üéì Your class: D.Pharma (2024‚Äì2026)`

Submit button stays **disabled** until all required academic fields are filled.

### Google Sign-In
Redirected to `/complete-profile` where they fill:
- **Academic Details panel**: Batch, Session From/To year pickers, Roll Number, class preview
- **4 mandatory document uploads** (same as email users)

---

## Validation & Uniqueness

| Check | Where enforced |
|---|---|
| `sessionFrom < sessionTo` | Frontend (Session To dropdown filtered) + Backend |
| Roll number unique per class | DB compound index + API pre-check with human-readable error |
| All 4 docs required | Frontend (button disabled) + API response 400 |
| File type explicit | Extension from filename, never from URL |
| File size ‚â§ 5MB | Backend per-file check |

Duplicate roll error example:
> `Roll Number "01" is already taken in D.Pharma (2024-2026). Please check with your administrator.`

---

## API Changes

| Endpoint | Change |
|---|---|
| `POST /api/auth/register` | Accepts `sessionFrom, sessionTo, rollNumber`; creates Class doc |
| `POST /api/auth/complete-profile` | Google users: creates Class, sets `classId/rollNumber` |
| `GET /api/public/batches` | Unchanged |
| `GET /api/public/classes` | **New** ‚Äî lists classes for a given batch |
| `GET /api/student/dashboard` | Returns `className, rollNumber, sessionFrom, sessionTo` |
| `GET /api/admin/students` | Filters: `batchId, classId, sessionFrom, sessionTo, rollNumber` |

